<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>WavePlay - Your Music Universe</title>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #8E2DE2;
      --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, #8E2DE2 0%, #4A00E0 100%);
      --secondary: #121212;
      --light: #f0f0f0;
      --accent: #00c6ff;
      --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--secondary);
      color: white;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    
    .waveform {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.07;
      pointer-events: none;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        var(--primary),
        var(--primary) 2px,
        transparent 2px,
        transparent 20px
      );
    }
    
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero-circle {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      opacity: 0.5;
      filter: blur(60px);
    }
    
    .hero-circle:nth-child(1) {
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      top: -100px;
      left: -200px;
    }
    
    .hero-circle:nth-child(2) {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      bottom: -50px;
      right: -100px;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent), #4A00E0);
    }
    
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 30px 0;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .logo i {
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    
    .hero-title span {
      display: block;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    
    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    
    .features {
      padding: 100px 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .section-title span {
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .section-subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    
    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .feature-desc {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .cta {
      padding: 100px 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .cta-bg {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.1) 0%, rgba(74, 0, 224, 0.1) 100%);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    .floating-notes {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .note {
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0.1;
      animation: float 15s linear infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      10% {
        opacity: 0.1;
      }
      90% {
        opacity: 0.1;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(360deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }
    
    .album-display {
      position: relative;
      height: 200px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    
    .album {
      position: absolute;
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .album:nth-child(1) {
      background-image: url("/api/placeholder/150/150");
      transform: translateX(-125%) rotate(-15deg);
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .album:nth-child(2) {
      background-image: url("/api/placeholder/150/150");
      transform: translateX(-60%) rotate(-5deg);
      z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .album:nth-child(3) {
      background-image: url("/api/placeholder/150/150");
      transform: translateX(0) rotate(0deg);
      z-index: 3;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
    }
    
    .album:nth-child(4) {
      background-image: url("/api/placeholder/150/150");
      transform: translateX(60%) rotate(5deg);
      z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .album:nth-child(5) {
      background-image: url("/api/placeholder/150/150");
      transform: translateX(125%) rotate(15deg);
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
      
      .btn-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
      }
      
      .album {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
      }
      
      .album:nth-child(3) {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
      }
      
      .album:nth-child(1), .album:nth-child(5) {
        display: none;
      }
      
      .album:nth-child(2) {
        transform: translateX(-70%) rotate(-5deg);
      }
      
      .album:nth-child(4) {
        transform: translateX(70%) rotate(5deg);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Animated background -->
  <div class="waveform"></div>
  
  <!-- Hero section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-circle"></div>
    <div class="hero-circle"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">
          <i class="fas fa-waveform-path"></i>WavePlay
        </div>
      </header>
      
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Your Music, <span>Amplified</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Stream your favorite tracks, create personalized playlists, and discover new artists in a seamless audio experience.</p>
        
        <div class="album-display">
          <div class="album" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511671782779-c97d3d27a1d4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="album" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497032628192-86f99bcd76bc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="album" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511671782779-c97d3d27a1d4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="album" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507874457470-272b3c8d8ee2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="album" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544785349-c4a5301826fd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80');"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="btn-group">
          <% if (!locals.user) { %>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-headphones"></i> Login</a>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Register</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/songs" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> Browse Songs</a>
            <a href="/songs/upload/new" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt"></i> Upload Music</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Features section -->
  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Amazing <span>Features</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Experience music like never before with our powerful set of features designed for true music lovers</p>
      
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-headphones-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">High Quality Audio</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Stream crystal-clear sound with our advanced audio processing technology. Hear every detail as the artist intended.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-list"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Custom Playlists</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Create, organize and share your perfect music collections for any mood, occasion or activity.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-upload"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Unlimited Uploads</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Upload your personal music library and access it from anywhere, anytime, on any device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA section -->
  <section class="cta">
    <div class="cta-bg"></div>
    <div class="floating-notes">
      <i class="fas fa-music note" style="top: 10%; left: 15%; animation-duration: 20s;"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-music note" style="top: 30%; left: 85%; animation-duration: 15s;"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-music note" style="top: 50%; left: 25%; animation-duration: 18s;"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-music note" style="top: 70%; left: 70%; animation-duration: 22s;"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-note note" style="top: 20%; left: 40%; animation-duration: 19s;"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-note note" style="top: 60%; left: 55%; animation-duration: 21s;"></i>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Start Your <span>Musical Journey</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Join thousands of music fans already enjoying our platform. It only takes a minute to get started.</p>
      
      <% if (!locals.user) { %>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Get Started Now</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/songs" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> Listen Now</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <script>
    // Randomly position and animate musical notes
    const notes = document.querySelectorAll('.note');
    notes.forEach(note => {
      note.style.left = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
      note.style.animationDelay = `${Math.random() * 10}s`;
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>